lead_paragraph: The United States will renew their rivalry with Mexico in a World Cup qualifier on Friday, three days after the U.S. presidential election brought the relationship between the two nations to the forefront in a bitterly divisive campaign.

headline.print_headline: U.S. and Mexico Meet on Heels of Trump Victory
headline.main: U.S. and Mexico Meet on Heels of Trump Victory
